=== Critical Threshold: Bearability

The goal is _not_ cure or remission within 2 weeks—that is unrealistic. The goal is to reduce suffering from *unbearable* to *bearable*, buying time to pursue longer-term fundamental treatments (Section @sec:medium-term-recovery).

For patients considering medical assistance in dying, this reduction in suffering can mean the difference between ending life and continuing to fight for recovery.

